* Kamil, Jill. &quot;Coptic Egypt: History and a Guide.&quot; Revised Ed. American University in Cairo Press, 1990.
* Meinardus, Otto Friedrich August. &quot;Two Thousand Years of Coptic Christianity&quot; (2010)
