* Van Doorn-Harder, Nelly. &quot;Finding a Platform: Studying the Copts in the 19th and 20th Centuries&quot; &quot;International Journal of Middle East Studies&quot; (Aug 2010) 42#3 pp 479‚Äì482. Historiography
