==In popular culture==
Petah Tikva is referenced in the Tony Award‚Äìwinning 2016 musical &quot;The Band&#x27;s Visit&quot; as the main plot derives from a mix-up between the city and the fictional town of &quot;Bet Hatikva&quot; in the Negev Desert of southern Israel.

Petah Tikva is known for being a part of a satirical conspiracy theory which claims that it does not exist, much like the German Bielefeld conspiracy. &quot;Free Petah Tikvah&quot; became a meme during 2023.

